          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/post-rocker/" class=" " title="孬爷爷">孬爷爷</a>
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="12546463">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">和画家一样，黑客只是怀有一门特殊技艺、有创造天赋的普通人。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-04-26 12:35</span>
                  
                </p>
